properties.name: Boston Opera House
properties.description: Posted by Comicpearl539 Washington Street, Boston, MA, United StatesThe Boston Opera House is located at 539 Washington Street, in the heart of Boston\'s theatre district. Opened in 1928, the venue has been host to everything from extrvagant vaudeville to a movie screen. Recent efforts to revitalize the venue have cemeted the Opera House\'s place in the culture of Boston. Today the Opera House hosts hit Broadway musicals, popular and alternative musicians, along with the occasional Opera. If you are interested in advertising on BostonOperaHouse.com, please contact us. Boston Opera House.com is a resource for information about the Opera House past and present, as well as a place to find tickets to every event hosted therein.
